"review_level": "None",
"content": "<p>Picking up grain or fruit left by the harvesters.</p>\n<h2>Commands concerning gleaning</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Lev19:9-Lev19:10\">LEV 19:9–19:10</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Lev23:22\">LEV 23:22</a></p>\n<h2>People involved with gleaning</h2>\n<p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ruth2:2-Ruth2:3\">RUT 2:2–2:3</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ruth2:7-Ruth2:8\">RUT 2:7–2:8</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ruth2:15-Ruth2:23\">RUT 2:15–2:23</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Job24:6\">JOB 24:6</a></p>\n<h2>Gleaning used figuratively, to mean something insignificant</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa17:5-Isa17:6\">ISA 17:5–17:6</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Judg8:2\">JDG 8:2</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa24:13\">ISA 24:13</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer6:9\">JER 6:9</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mic7:1\">MIC 7:1</a></p>",
